snippet.title: Diana's Halloween Candy Adventure
snippet.description:
In this Halloween special, Diana takes a special candy adventure! 
Diana and her friend search for keys in 6 Halloween escape rooms to activate the candy making machine.
Be sure to watch all the way to the end to see what happens!


Thanks for watching!
